{"tid":1062084,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞VS曼城？歐聯8強抽籤內定？","createTime":"2019-03-15T00:39:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T14:13:36.000Z","uid":153600,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6f73ef6861cefc6d76551fa51086d25a72daffac","tid":1062084,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T00:39:16.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsadB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=9b64a064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】網上流傳一張歐聯8強抽籤結果的相片，據悉來自歐聯高層，令抽籤內定的傳言再現。<br />\n<br />\n一名叫HurriKane的網友周四在Twitter上載一張聲稱來自歐聯高層的相片，相中是歐聯8強的抽籤結果：曼聯對熱刺、利物浦對阿積士、巴塞隆拿對曼城、祖雲達斯對波圖。該網民表示該高層意外把結果放上網後迅速刪除，但已經被網民「留底」。<br />\n<br />\n該張相片再次引起球迷對抽籤造馬的懷疑，網友留言寫道：「大家記住這個抽籤結果，看與周五抽籤是否吻合？」另一網友質疑：「這是抽籤的結果嗎？」網絡時代「呃like」至上，這次會不會是HurriKane吸引網民注意的技倆？<br />\n<br />\nHurriKane看到英國傳媒報道他的「post」時，才知道自己受到人們關注，他的「post」也獲得167個「like」，甚至有網民留言問他抽籤的事情，一下子變成了網紅。"},{"pid":"2685c8db6f8aef5678e1dd7af86ff0978bb3589d","tid":1062084,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T00:40:56.000Z","msg":"最域屌打巴塞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9360a9e2e5dcd0ffc88a1b1cb5bfa7abc6ed339b","tid":1062084,"uid":77788,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T00:42:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de954b873933b44b4358237891b8c09271056564","tid":1062084,"uid":39133,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T00:43:09.000Z","msg":"呢d內定紙咁多年黎有無全中過1次"},{"pid":"27eaca1d08aaf898f33b4c5ec47ef32effab06b5","tid":1062084,"uid":162906,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T00:45:21.000Z","msg":"利物浦今年又入決賽."},{"pid":"0c0c23f9b70cc5745ef8a25922cb0113fd7e9d23","tid":1062084,"uid":9931,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T00:53:08.000Z","msg":"牙朗又有上上籤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔計呀"},{"pid":"bc56e6